Package: maritalAffairs
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Exploring Marital Satisfaction and Extramarital Affairs
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "David",
           family = "Sanchez",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "davidsanche@usf.edu")
Description: 
    Provides functions to summarize, model, and visualize the relationship between 
    marital satisfaction, demographics, and reported extramarital affairs based on 
    a classic survey dataset of married individuals.
